data.description: Priced to sell! Come view this fixer home in Bend, OR on .30 Acre!!  This property is a canvas waiting for your creative touch. Whether it's a modern kitchen, a cozy living room, or a spacious backyard oasis, the possibilities are endless. Nestled in the heart of Bend, you'll enjoy the best of both worlds - the tranquility of a cul-de-sac and the vibrant lifestyle. Bend is known for its outdoor recreational opportunities, craft breweries, and a welcoming atmosphere. It's the perfect place to call home! Don't miss this fantastic opportunity to make this house your own. The price is right, and the potential is limitless.
